narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Southeast Kansas Mental Health Center is a Pediatrics provider based in Humboldt, KS. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $66.2M in Medicaid payments across 441K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $66.2M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
